metadata.name: Li Lizhi saw the queen
metadata.description:
their own meaning out of the palace, he also want to go out of the palace, but afraid of Wei Hao ah, so many days did not see yourself, Wei Hao certainly will not let go of their own, do not know how to blame themselves.



"You don't know if Wei Hao is responsible for this until you leave the palace. Besides, if your father knows that he bought it from Wei Hao, and our royal family also has shares in it, he won't be so angry. If not, your brother will surely be punished this time." Queen Changsun said to Li Lizhi.
